<D>__{solitary. a week. make sure he takes his bible.}
<C>__{con}
<D>__{too goddamn dark to read down there.}
<C>__{norton}
<D>__{add another week for blasphemy.}
<A>__{the man is taken away. norton's gaze goes up.}
